description:
If you live, work, or visit Boston, Chicago, Dallas, South Florida, Houston, Los Angeles, New York, Philadelphia, San Francisco or Washington D.C. then these pocket maps are for you - - A must for the traveler and commuter.

Fast loading subway & rail maps of the 
Boston 'T'
Chicago Rail L System
Dallas Dart 
Houston MetroRail 
Los Angeles Metro 
New York Subways 
Philadelphia Center City 
San Francisco Bart  
Washington D.C Metro

Zoom and pan each map.  Save your favorite map preference for one tap loading of that map.  Internet not required.  All maps are available all the times.  

Additional maps will be added in the future.  Email GeezerNetwork with you favorite map suggestion.  

This app is MAPS only.  No schedules or real time data included.  

Interested in finding the closest subway station to your location in New York or Boston?  This map  application is integrated with TMaps NY Closest Subway and the Closest T applications.  Both of these applications are available in the Palm catalog and can be added at any time.
